name: Fly High - Ball Bouncing Endless Fun Game
name_original: Fly High - Ball Bouncing Endless Fun Game
description:
Fly High- One more interesting game from Photon Games.A new type
of challenge it is a simple one touch controls game, touch to fly the ball

and avoid hitting the closing blocks. Be quick to pass between the

obstacles.
Set a high score and challenge your friends to beat your score. Enjoy

the game-play
